    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-101">將 ASP.NET 網頁檢視狀態儲存在 Web 用戶端上的隱藏 HTML 項目。</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="cf9c3-101">Stores ASP.NET page view state on the Web client in a hidden HTML element.</span>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-102">ASP.NET 頁面可以儲存<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>之間原本就是無狀態的 HTTP 要求和回應處理及做任何網頁所需的狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-102">ASP.NET pages can store <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> state between the inherently stateless HTTP request and response required to process and serve any Web page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-103">此狀態稱為 「 檢視狀態 」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-103">This state is called "view state".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-104">用來儲存頁面和它的控制項檢視狀態的預設機制是在一或多個`<hidden>`從 Web 伺服器向用戶端頁面中包含的 HTML 欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-104">The default mechanism used to store view state for a page and its controls is in one or more `<hidden>` HTML fields included in the page that is served to a client from a Web server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-105"><xref:System.Web.UI.Page>類別可以使用<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister>類別來進行這項工作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-105">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> class to do this work.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> 會實作<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A>並<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>類別，讓<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>可以儲存在狀態`<hidden>`名為"__VIEWSTATE"Web 用戶端上的 HTML 項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> class so that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> can store state in a `<hidden>` HTML element named "__VIEWSTATE" on a Web client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-107">當用戶端要求相同的頁面從網頁伺服器 （回傳）`<hidden>`剖析項目並將其轉換成狀態資訊的 ASP.NET。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-107">When the client requests the same page from the Web server (a postback), the `<hidden>` element is parsed and converted to state information by ASP.NET.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-108">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>要求的執行個體都有相關聯<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter>類別，它會擷取<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>物件，此配接器使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-108">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> instance that is requested has an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter> class, it retrieves the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object from this adapter using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-109">配接器可以覆寫<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A>方法來傳回<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>一些特定的用戶端支援的方式儲存頁面和控制項狀態的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-109">Adapters can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method to return a <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object that stores page and control state in some way that a specific client supports.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-110">比方說，<xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister>類別會在 Web 伺服器上，而不是用戶端，以減少必須傳送，而且可能有限記憶體和頻寬的用戶端上儲存資訊的儲存頁面和控制項的狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-110">For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister> class stores page and controls' state on the Web server, instead of the client, to decrease the amount of information that must be sent and stored on a client that has potentially limited memory and bandwidth.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-111">「 _VIEWSTATE"的大小上限`<hidden>`HTML 項目可以透過設定<xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A>屬性或透過<xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A>組態設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-111">The maximum size of the "_VIEWSTATE" `<hidden>` HTML element can be set through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> property or through the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> configuration setting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-112">當設定這個值，而"_VIEWSTATE 」 項目的長度會超過最大長度時，會將內容分成多個 「 _VIEWSTATE"項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-112">When this value is set and the length of the "_VIEWSTATE" element would exceed the maximum length, the content is divided into multiple "_VIEWSTATE" elements.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-113">下列程式碼範例示範如何繫結<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListBox>與資料庫中的資料控制項<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource>控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-113">The following code example demonstrates how to bind a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListBox> control to data in a database with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource> control.</span></span>  
  
 [!code-aspx-csharp[System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource_1sql#1](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_WebNet/System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource_1sql/CS/sql1cs.aspx#1)]
 [!code-aspx-vb[System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource_1sql#1](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_WebNet/System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource_1sql/VB/sql1vb.aspx#1)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9c3-114">檢視範例資料頁，任何檢視狀態儲存<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister>類別中`<hidden>`名為"__VIEWSTATE"的 HTML 項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9c3-114">When the example page is viewed, any view state is stored by the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> class in a `<hidden>` HTML element named "__VIEWSTATE".</span></span>  
  
```  
<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">  
<HTML>  
  <BODY>  
    <form name="_ctl0" method="post" action="sample.aspx" id="_ctl0">  
  
      <input type="hidden" name="__VIEWSTATE" value="" />  
  
      <select size="4" name="ListBox1" id="ListBox1">      
        <option value="Buchanan">Buchanan</option>  
        <option value="Callahan">Callahan</option>  
        <option value="Davolio">Davolio</option>  
        <option value="Dodsworth">Dodsworth</option>  
        <option value="Fuller">Fuller</option>  
        <option value="King">King</option>  
        <option value="Leverling">Leverling</option>  
        <option value="Suyama">Suyama</option>  
      </select>  
  
    </form>  
  </BODY>  
</HTML>  
```  
  
 ]]></format>
